title: Wall Street Breakfast July 8: June Jobs Report, Temperature Check of the Economy
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: June jobs report will be parsed for signs of labor market cooling. Twitter drops off 7.5% on report Musk's purchase bid in jeopardy. Spirit Airlines postpones Frontier holder vote as talks progress with JetBlue. Former Japan Prime Minister Shinzo Abe shot and killed. Catch today’s WSB article here.
